snippet.title: Good Company - Multiplayer Trailer
snippet.description:
Good Company sets players up to build their business from a scrappy upstart to the best tech corporation in the country. Getting there won't be easy -- entrepreneurs will need to be savvy about managing staff, optimizing supply chains, and finding new ways to keep the cash flowing.

Good Company will launch on June 21, 2022 on Epic Games Store, Steam, and GOG for $24.99 / €22.99 / £19.99.

For more information, please visit https://www.goodcompanygame.com 

Good Company on:
Epic: https://store.epicgames.com/en-US/p/good-company
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/911430/Good_Company/
